
zktools

zktools is a collection of open Bash and C code designed for system security and system management for Zero Knowledge Network (ZKN) Edge Node 400 and compatible devices. These tools help automate security configurations, manage system resources, and enhance overall system integrity. The tools are a work in progress and more features will be added in time.

Features

Automates system security configurations

Provides system management utilities

Enhances security for Zero Knowledge Network environments

Streamlines administrative tasks

Installation

Clone the repository and set up executable permissions:

sudo apt update
sudo apt install dialog libpcap-dev libncurses-dev -y
https://github.com/infinitydaemon/zktools.git
cd zktools
chmod +x *
gcc -o packet_sniff packet_sniff.c -lpcap -lncurses
sudo cp * /usr/local/bin

Use "zktools" for main menu.

